3:T81a,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"What is the best fruit billing software in India?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"MandiGrow is the best fruit billing software in India for wholesale traders and commission agents. It is built specifically for the fruits and vegetable trade — handling lots, grades, varieties, weight, commission, market fees and GST natively. Unlike Tally or Zoho, MandiGrow was designed from Day 1 for the mandi."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Does MandiGrow support perishable inventory tracking?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. MandiGrow tracks perishable inventory in real time — by variety, grade, lot, and warehouse location. Auto-valuation accounts for weight loss and wastage. Stock positions update instantly with every purchase or sale."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Is MandiGrow a good vegetable billing software for wholesale traders?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. MandiGrow is specifically built for vegetable wholesale traders — supporting purchase bills from farmers, sales invoices to buyers, and multi-variety stock tracking across locations. GST, Mandi Tax, and commission are all automated."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can MandiGrow handle multi-warehouse fruit and vegetable stock?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. MandiGrow supports multi-location inventory tracking. If you operate across multiple godowns or market locations, your stock positions, valuations, and movements are visible in a single dashboard."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How is MandiGrow different from Tally for fruit and vegetable traders?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Tally is a general accounting tool. MandiGrow is purpose-built for the fruit and vegetable trade. MandiGrow handles lots, crates, weight, commission, hamali, palledari, market fees, mandi khata, and patti generation — all of which require custom workarounds in Tally. MandiGrow is the leading Tally alternative for mandi traders in India."}}]}0:{"rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[["$","main",null,{"className":"min-h-screen bg-[#f7fbf3] text-gray-900 pt-20","children":[["$","$L2",null,{}],["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$3"}}],["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Home\",\"item\":\"https://www.mandigrow.com\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Fruit & Vegetable Billing Software\",\"item\":\"https://www.mandigrow.com/fruit-vegetable-billing\"}]}"}}],["$","section",null,{"className":"max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 pt-16 pb-16","children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"text-emerald-700 font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-xs mb-4","children":"Fruit & Vegetable Billing Software · India"}],["$","h1",null,{"className":"text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black tracking-tighter leading-[1.05] mb-6","children":["$","$L4",null,{"tKey":"seo_pages.fruit_h1","fallback":"Fruit & Vegetable Billing Software for Indian Wholesale Traders"}]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-xl text-gray-700 max-w-3xl mb-4","children":["$","$L4",null,{"tKey":"seo_pages.fruit_p","fallback":"MandiGrow is India's #1 fruit and vegetable billing software for wholesale traders, commission agents, and mandi operators. Manage purchase bills, sales invoices, perishable stock tracking, GST compliance, and party payments — all in one cloud platform."}]}],"$L5","$L6"]}],"$L7","$L8","$L9","$La","$Lb"]}],["$Lc","$Ld","$Le"],"$Lf"]}],"isPartial":false,"staleTime":300,"varyParams":null,"buildId":"0tdL6ydBkUN_zxHFnYlXu"}
